<paragraph id="8BDC16394921FFDAFEB6FBD9FBEADBBC" blockId="6.[264,1325,284,1239]" box="[312,1076,1133,1159]" pageId="6" pageNumber="53">
Etymology. The specific name refers to the 
<typeStatus id="54D8A89B4921FFDAFCB6FBD9FCB4DBBC" box="[824,874,1133,1159]" pageId="6" pageNumber="53">type</typeStatus>
